# {PROJECT_TITLE} - Memory Verification ({SESSION_DATE})

Two ways to verify this pack: the automated check (fast, objective) and the
recall test (confirms the memory is actually useful next session).

## Automated check

Run the validator from the skill (or any copy of it):

```bash
python validate_memory.py --dir "{PACK_DIRNAME}"
```

It confirms every expected file exists, the JSON and YAML parse, and the
required keys are present. Fix anything it flags before integrating.

