## Recall test (the real test)

Open a fresh session, load this pack, and ask:

- [ ] "What were we working on?" -> recalls project + current phase
- [ ] "What did we decide and why?" -> recalls key decisions with reasoning
- [ ] "How do I like information presented?" -> recalls your working preferences
- [ ] "What's left to do?" -> recalls next tasks / open threads
- [ ] "Continue where we left off." -> picks up without re-explaining

If any of these miss, the gap is almost always in the summary or project-context
file. Add the missing detail there and re-run the automated check.
